Invocation Name: feel goodies
des: When you need a encouragement, you can ask Alexa to Open Feel-Goodies® to hear positive sayings. Feel-Goodies® are a way to integrate successful powerful beliefs into your consciousness. Positive thoughts lead to a positive life. Feel-Goodies® through Alexa Skills allow you Ask Feel-Goodies to say something and you will hear Alexa remind you how wonderful you already are. Feel-Goodies® are distilled from many spiritual, sellf-help and motivational truths. Please be sure to use Feel-Goodies with an "s" on the end after Alexa, ask, do, open or tell.
